OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,7,FMichelle O'Neill has called for a
OL,8,F"different approach" from incoming
OL,9,Fprime minister Andy Burnham.
OL,11,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson agreed that
OL,12,FMr Burnham needs to "deliver a change
OL,13,Fof direction", urging him to show "an
OL,14,Funambiguous commitment" to Northern
OL,15,FIreland's position in the UK.
OL,17,FMr Burnham was officially made the
OL,18,FLabour Party leader at a special
OL,19,Fconference at the Trades Union
OL,20,FCongress headquarters in central
OL,21,FLondon on Friday.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]tD@UOUuD@MO]uD@cOUvD@WO]
