OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,FHe will replace Sir Keir Starmer as
OL,7,Fprime minister next week, vowing to
OL,8,Fgive people "hope back".
OL,10,FThe former mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,11,Fhas been a vocal supporter of more
OL,12,Fdevolved powers to English regions.
OL,14,FIn his acceptance speech, he said: "We
OL,15,Fwill take power back from Westminster
OL,16,Fand Whitehall, and give it to the
OL,17,Fplace where you live ` more power over
OL,18,Flife's essentials, so you can make
OL,19,Fthem work better and more affordable
OL,20,Ffor people."
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@WO]vD@dOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
