OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784531891
OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe First Minister and vice-president
OL,7,Fof Sinn Fein said she wishes the
OL,8,FMakerfield MP well on becoming Labour
OL,9,Fleader and stands "ready to work
OL,10,Fconstructively with him".
OL,12,F"A different approach is needed from
OL,13,Fthe British Government," she said.
OL,15,F"Successive British governments have
OL,16,Fimplemented policies that have been
OL,17,Fcatastrophic for ordinary people.
OL,26,@oD@JrrqD@SOUrD@XO]tD@AOUuD@XO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
