PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784531891
OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"They have cut vital public services,
OL,7,Fdeepened inequalities, and left
OL,8,Ffamilies struggling through a cost-of-
OL,9,Fliving crisis while a small elite
OL,10,Fcontinues to accumulate enormous
OL,11,Fwealth.
OL,13,F"I look forward to meeting with Andy
OL,14,FBurnham when he takes up the role as
OL,15,FBritish prime minister.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
