OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784531891
OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"I will make the case for fair funding
OL,7,Ffor public services, action on the
OL,8,Fcost-of-living crisis, and full
OL,9,Frespect for our democratic right to
OL,10,Fdetermine our own future here on the
OL,11,Fisland of Ireland.
OL,13,F"The interests of all the people of
OL,14,FIreland will be best served when we
OL,15,Fhave full control of our own affairs
OL,16,Fin a new and united Ireland."
OL,18,FMr Robinson said Mr Burnham needs to
OL,19,Fshow "an unambiguous commitment to our
OL,20,Fplace within the United Kingdom".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@]O]{D@FOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
