FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784531891
OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"It means securing our borders,
OL,7,Frestoring Northern Ireland's full and
OL,8,Funfettered place within the UK
OL,9,Finternal market, and ensuring every
OL,10,Fcitizen and every business is treated
OL,11,Fequally wherever they live in our
OL,12,Fcountry," he said.
OL,14,FHe added: "The public will judge Andy
OL,15,FBurnham not by speeches or social
OL,16,Fmedia videos, but by whether he has
OL,17,Fthe courage to reject Labour's recent
OL,18,Ffailures.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
