FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784531891
OL,3,CMichelle O'Neill and Gavin Robinson
OL,4,Ccall for change from Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"Northern Ireland needs a Prime
OL,7,FMinister who believes in the Union,
OL,8,Fbacks those who work hard, secures our
OL,9,Fborders, invests in our national
OL,10,Fdefence and governs with conviction
OL,11,Frather than chasing the latest
OL,12,Fpolitical fashion.
OL,14,F"The opportunity to change course is
OL,15,Fthere. It is now for Andy Burnham to
OL,16,Fprove he is prepared to take it."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
